OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK fruit picking like      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprison, says migrant worker
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A South African woman has described    
OL,6, working as a fruit picker on farms in  
OL,7, the south of England as "slave labour".
OL,9,F"We weren't viewed as humans," Sybil   
OL,10,FMsezane told a House of Lords          
OL,11,Fcommittee.                             
OL,13,FShe said workers were addressed by     
OL,14,Fnumbers, rather than names, as if they 
OL,15,Fwere in prison, forced to work 18 hour 
OL,16,Fdays and live in overcrowded caravans. 
OL,18,FIf they complained to bosses they were 
OL,19,Fthreatened with deportation, the Lords 
OL,20,Fhorticultural committee was told.      
